*Kupim* šolju kafe (I will buy a cup of coffee).
*Kupila* sam novu haljinu (I bought a new dress).
*Kupuje* on knjigu (He is buying a book).
*Kupio* sam novi džemper (I bought a new sweater).
*Kupujući* novi automobil, morao je da odloži druga putovanja (Buying a new car, he had to postpone other trips).